                "citation_count": 12,
                "reference_count": 13,
                "abstract": "We give a necessary and sufficient condition for the addition of a collection of disjoint bypasses to a convex surface to be universally tight - namely the nonexistence of a polygonal region which we call a virtual pinwheel. AMS Classification 57M50; 53C15",
